NAC Web Interface

Version 0.1, 05.09.06/sb


To install get the latest sources:
  svn xxxx

Install apache.

Then configure apache:
- create /etc/apache2/conf.d/vmps.conf
  Alias /vmps /opt/vmps/web1
        <Directory /opt/vmps/web1/>
          Options none
          Order deny,allow
          #allow from 127.0.0.1
          #allow from 10.85.
          allow from all
        </Directory>

- restart apache
    rcpache restart

- point the webbrowser at http://SERVER/vmps


